Lamborghini from the future!

This is the Lamborghini Terzo Millennio. 🌟 This is what Lamborghini thinks their first electric car will look like. What's cool is they've teamed up with the best brains at Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT) to develop some incredible technologies like self-healing carbon fiber. 😱 They've also thought of a new way to create sound for an electric car...! 👉👉👉Because this vid gets interrupted, please check out my full review on YouTube. There's so much going on with this car! Special thanks to @mitjaborkert and @lamborghini for arranging this shoot.

World’s Only Street Legal Converted Maserati MC12 Corsa!

This Maserati was made for the track, but the owner converted it in to a street legal MC12 Corsa... for 400k! Only 12 Corsa's were made, and this is the only street legal one in the world.
Special thanks to @continentaltiresglobal & @edocompetition_official for letting me get behind the wheel!
